OL,4,CSir Lenny Henry: Survey shows racism is
OL,5,Ca stain on entertainment industry
OL,6, More than half of all actors from
OL,7, ethnic minorities have directly
OL,8, experienced racism in the workplace, a
OL,9, major new study has revealed.
OL,11,FThe UK survey of more than 1,300 actors
OL,12,Ffound that 64% had experienced racist
OL,13,Fstereotyping during an audition, while
OL,14,F55% suffered racist behaviour at work.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, 71% said hair and make-up
OL,17,Fdepartments had been unable to cater to
OL,18,Ftheir heritage, hair or skin tone.
OL,20,FSir Lenny Henry called the findings a
OL,21,F"stain against the entire industry".
